how do i add a buddy to my list in pidgin stanford answers stanford university stanford answers how do i add a buddy to my list in pidgin categories accounts and ids administrative applications anti virus and security computer operating systems connecting to the network desktop hardware and support email and calendar help desk restricted information on it services software at stanford stanford hospital and clinics telephones and cable tv unix systems and software web services user login login with your sunet id home how do i add a buddy to my list in pidgin search this site choose buddies add buddy select your stanford edu account then enter your buddy's username in the form sunetid stanford edu select the desired group and click add note that your buddy will have to authorize you before his or her account is active in your buddy list to add a buddy in pidgin in pidgin choose buddies add buddy select your stanford edu account from the pull down menu your stanford account displays by default if no other accounts are active enter the buddy's username use the format sunetid stanford edu do not use a sunetid_alias stanford edu address optional enter an alias name for that person select the desired group for your buddy optional you can put your buddy in more than one group if you like click add note that your buddy's account will not be active in your buddy list until she or he authorizes you similarly you must authorize requests to have your account appear in others buddy lists stanford instant messaging stanford university 450 serra mall stanford california 94305 650 723 2300 terms of use copyright complaints
